        <abstract>
            <p>Glad to hear of Ernst Haeckel’s reception in Vienna.</p> 
<p>R. Virchow’s address ["Liberty of science", <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> 17 (1877–8): 72–4, 92–4, 111–13] very arrogant.</p> 
            <p>Sorry to hear of death of Arthur Lane.</p>
        </abstract>
